== Dice of Doom

Implementing the game from *Land of Lisp* in JS/Coffeescript/Node

=== play

Requires node => http://nodejs.org/
along with the coffeescript and underscore libraries.

These are easily installed with npm => http://npmjs.org/
$ npm install coffee-script && npm install underscore

on the command line:
$ coffee src/cli.coffee

start a server:
$ coffee src/server.coffee

=== next

Serve up over a node HTTP server.

=== history 

v0.0.1
Basic human vs. human play.

v0.0.2
Basic computer AI.

v0.0.3
Lazy evaluation of game trees. Basic heuristics for AI game
board rating.
